Drux Lord
=========

Desription
==========

This is a Linux clone of Drug Lord 2 game (http://www.geekhideout.com/druglord2.shtml)
I write this because I like this game, it is stupid and funny. I also want to add
and improve anything that looks cool to me.


Build
=====

Consult your distribution for GTK+ 2 development library, GNU C compiler and GNU Make.
No autotools and configuration script.


